 County]]||[[the Football League|Football League]]||align=right|46\n|- bgcolor=ccffcc\n|[[Hereford United F.C.|Hereford United]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|26 (29)\n|- \n|[[Barrow A.F.C.|Barrow]]||[[the Football League|Football League]]||align=right|26 (20)\n|-\n|[[Bradford Park Avenue A.F.C.|Bradford Park Avenue]]||[[Northern Premier League]]||align=right|1\n|-\n|[[Cambridge City F.C.|Cambridge City]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|1\n|-\n|[[Wimbledon F.C.|Wimbledon]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|1\n|-\n|[[Bangor City F.C.|Bangor City]]||[[Northern Premier League]]||align=right|0\n|-\n|[[Bedford Town F.C.|Bedford Town]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|0\n|-\n|[[Boston United F.C.|Boston United]]||[[Northern Premier League]]||align=right|0\n|-\n|[[Hillingdon Borough F.C.|Hillingdon Borough]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|0\n|-\n|[[Romford F.C.|Romford]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|0\n|-\n|[[Telford United F.C.|Telford United]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|0\n|-\n|[[Wigan Athletic F.C.|Wigan Athletic]]||[[Northern Premier League]]||align=right|0\n|-\n|[[Yeovil Town F.C.|Yeovil Town]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|0\n|}\n\n==References==\n*[http://www.rsssf.com/tablese/engsouthernleaghist.html RSSF \u2013 Southern Football League archive]\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Southern Football League seasons}}\n{{1971\u201372 in English football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1971-72 Southern Football League}}\n[[Category:Southern Football League seasons]]\n[[Category:1971\u201372 in English football leagues|S]]\n", "text_old": "The '''1971\u201372 [[Southern Football League]] season''' was the 69th in the history of the league, an English [[Association football|football]] competition.\n\nAt the end of the previous season Division One was split into divisions One North and One South with 14 new clubs joining the league.\n\n[[Chelmsford City F.C.|Chelmsford City]] won the championship, winning their third Southern League title, whilst [[Burton Albion F.C.|Burton Albion]], [[Kettering Town F.C.|Kettering Town]], [[Ramsgate Athletic F.C.|Ramsgate Athletic]] and [[Waterlooville F.C.|Waterlooville]] were all promoted to the Premier Division. Eight Southern League clubs applied to join [[the Football League]] at the end of the season, [[Hereford United F.C.|Hereford United]] was elected in favour of [[Barrow A.F.C.|Barrow]] after a tie in the first vote.\n\n==Premier Division==\nThe Premier Division consisted of 22 clubs, including 18 clubs from the [[1970\u201371 Southern Football League#Premier Division|previous season]] and four new clubs, promoted from Division One:\n*[[Folkestone F.C.|Folkestone]]\n*[[Gravesend & Northfleet F.C.|Gravesend & Northfleet]]\n*[[Guildford City F.C.|Guildford City]]\n*[[Merthyr Tydfil F.C.|Merthyr Tydfil]]\n\n===League table===\n{{Infobox football league season\n|competition= Southern Football League<br>Premier Division\n|season=1971\u201372\n|winners= [[Chelmsford City F.C.|Chelmsford City]]\n|relegated= [[Bath City F.C.|Bath City]]<br>[[Gloucester City F.C.|Gloucester City]]<br>[[Merthyr Tydfil F.C.|Merthyr Tydfil]]\n|matches= 462\n|total goals= 1378\n|prevseason= [[1970\u201371 Southern Football League#Premier Division|1970\u201371]]\n|nextseason= [[1972\u201373 Southern Football League#Premier Division|1972\u201373]]\n}}\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=PR\n|use_goal_ratio=y\n|winpoints=2\n|section=Premier Division\n\n|team1=CHC|name_CHC=[[Chelmsford City F.C.|Chelmsford City]]\n|team2=HER|name_HER=[[Hereford United F.C.|Hereford United]]\n|team3=DOV|name_DOV=[[Dover F.C.|Dover]]\n|team4=BRN|name_BRN=[[Barnet F.C.|Barnet]]\n|team5=DAR|name_DAR=[[Dartford F.C.|Dartford]]\n|team6=WEY|name_WEY=[[Weymouth F.C.|Weymouth]]\n|team7=YEO|name_YEO=[[Yeovil Town F.C.|Yeovil Town]]\n|team8=HIL|name_HIL=[[Hillingdon Borough F.C.|Hillingdon Borough]]\n|team9=MAR|name_MAR=[[Margate F.C.|Margate]]\n|team10=WIM|name_WIM=[[Wimbledon F.C.|Wimbledon]]\n|team11=ROM|name_ROM=[[Romford F.C.|Romford]]\n|team12=GUI|name_GUI=[[Guildford City F.C.|Guildford City]]\n|team13=TEL|name_TEL=[[Telford United F.C.|Telford United]]\n|team14=NUN|name_NUN=[[Nuneaton Borough F.C.|Nuneaton Borough]]\n|team15=BED|name_BED=[[Bedford Town F.C.|Bedford Town]]\n|team16=WOR|name_WOR=[[Worcester City F.C.|Worcester City]]\n|team17=CMC|name_CMC=[[Cambridge City F.C.|Cambridge City]]\n|team18=FOL|name_FOL=[[Folkestone F.C.|Folkestone]]\n|team19=POO|name_POO=[[Poole Town F.C.|Poole Town]]\n|team20=BAT|name_BAT=[[Bath City F.C.|Bath City]]\n|team21=MER|name_MER=[[Merthyr Tydfil F.C.|Merthyr Tydfil]]\n|team22=GRA|name_GRA=[[Gravesend & Northfleet F.C.|Gravesend & Northfleet]]\n|win_CHC=28|draw_CHC=6|loss_CHC=8|gf_CHC=109|ga_CHC=46\n|win_HER=24|draw_HER=12|loss_HER=6|gf_HER=68|ga_HER=30\n|win_DOV=20|draw_DOV=11|loss_DOV=11|gf_DOV=67|ga_DOV=45\n|win_BRN=21|draw_BRN=7|loss_BRN=14|gf_BRN=80|ga_BRN=57\n|win_DAR=20|draw_DAR=8|loss_DAR=14|gf_DAR=75|ga_DAR=68\n|win_WEY=21|draw_WEY=5|loss_WEY=16|gf_WEY=69|ga_WEY=43\n|win_YEO=18|draw_YEO=11|loss_YEO=13|gf_YEO=67|ga_YEO=51\n|win_HIL=20|draw_HIL=6|loss_HIL=16|gf_HIL=64|ga_HIL=58\n|win_MAR=19|draw_MAR=8|loss_MAR=15|gf_MAR=74|ga_MAR=68\n|win_WIM=19|draw_WIM=7|loss_WIM=16|gf_WIM=75|ga_WIM=64\n|win_ROM=16|draw_ROM=13|loss_ROM=13|gf_ROM=54|ga_ROM=49\n|win_GUI=20|draw_GUI=5|loss_GUI=17|gf_GUI=71|ga_GUI=65\n|win_TEL=18|draw_TEL=7|loss_TEL=17|gf_TEL=83|ga_TEL=68\n|win_NUN=16|draw_NUN=10|loss_NUN=16|gf_NUN=46|ga_NUN=47\n|win_BED=16|draw_BED=9|loss_BED=17|gf_BED=85|ga_BED=66\n|win_WOR=17|draw_WOR=7|loss_WOR=18|gf_WOR=46|ga_WOR=57\n|win_CMC=12|draw_CMC=14|loss_CMC=16|gf_CMC=68|ga_CMC=71\n|win_FOL=14|draw_FOL=7|loss_FOL=21|gf_FOL=58|ga_FOL=64\n|win_POO=9|draw_POO=11|loss_POO=22|gf_POO=41|ga_POO=72\n|win_BAT=11|draw_BAT=4|loss_BAT=27|gf_BAT=45|ga_BAT=86|\n|win_MER=7|draw_MER=8|loss_MER=27|gf_MER=29|ga_MER=93\n|win_GRA=5|draw_GRA=6|loss_GRA=31|gf_GRA=30|ga_GRA=110\n\n|col_P=#D0F0C0|text_P=Elected to the [[1972\u201373 Football League#Fourth Division|Football League]]\n|result2=P\n|col_R1S=#FFCCCC|text_R1S=Relegated to [[1972\u201373 Southern Football League#Division One South|Division One South]]\n|result20=R1S|result22=R1S\n|col_R1N=#FFCCCC|text_R1N=Relegated to [[1972\u201373 Southern Football League#Division One North|Division One North]]\n|result21=R1N\n|update=complete\n|source=[http://fchd.info/lghist/south1972.htm fchd.com] [http://www.rsssf.com/tablese/engsouthernleaghist.html rsssf.com]\n|class_rules=1) points; 2) goal ratio.\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Division One North==\nDivision One North consisted of 18 clubs, including eight clubs from the [[1970\u201371 Southern Football League#Division One|previous season]] Division One and ten new clubs:\n*Three clubs relegated from the Premier Division:\n**[[Gloucester City F.C.|Gloucester City]]\n**[[Kettering Town F.C.|Kettering Town]]\n**[[King's Lynn F.C.|King's Lynn]]\n\n*Two clubs joined from the [[Metropolitan League]]:\n**[[Bletchley Town F.C.|Bletchley Town]]\n**[[Bury Town F.C.|Bury Town]]\n\n*Two clubs joined from the [[Midland Football League (1889)|Midland League]]:\n**[[Ilkeston Town F.C. (1945)|Ilkeston Town]]\n**[[Lockheed Leamington F.C.|Lockheed Leamington]]\n\n*Two clubs joined from the [[1970\u201371 West Midlands (Regional) League|West Midlands (Regional) League]]:\n**[[Stourbridge F.C.|Stourbridge]]\n**[[Wellingborough Town F.C.|Wellingborough Town]]\n\n*Plus:\n**[[Wealdstone F.C.|Wealdstone]], joined from the [[1970\u201371 Isthmian League|Isthmian League]]\n\n===League table===\n{{Infobox football league season\n|competition= Southern Football League<br>Division One North\n|season=1971\u201372\n|winners= [[Kettering Town F.C.|Kettering Town]]\n|promoted= [[Burton Albion F.C.|Burton Albion]]<br>[[Kettering Town F.C.|Kettering Town]]\n|matches= 306\n|total goals= 904\n|prevseason= [[1970\u201371 Southern Football League#Division One|1970\u201371]]\n|nextseason= [[1972\u201373 Southern Football League#Division One North|1972\u201373]]\n}}\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=PR\n|use_goal_ratio=y\n|winpoints=2\n|section=Division One North\n\n|team1=KET|name_KET=[[Kettering Town F.C.|Kettering Town]]\n|team2=BTA|name_BTA=[[Burton Albion F.C.|Burton Albion]]\n|team3=CHT|name_CHT=[[Cheltenham Town F.C.|Cheltenham Town]]\n|team4=RUG|name_RUG=[[Rugby Town F.C. (1945)|Rugby Town]]\n|team5=WEL|name_WEL=[[Wellingborough Town F.C.|Wellingborough Town]]\n|team6=STB|name_STB=[[Stourbridge F.C.|Stourbridge]]\n|team7=KIN|name_KIN=[[King's Lynn F.C.|King's Lynn]]\n|team8=COR|name_COR=[[Corby Town F.C.|Corby Town]]\n|team9=ILK|name_ILK=[[Ilkeston Town F.C. (1945)|Ilkeston Town]]\n|team10=BAN|name_BAN=[[Banbury United F.C.|Banbury United]]\n|team11=BRY|name_BRY=[[Bury Town F.C.|Bury Town]]\n|team12=WEA|name_WEA=[[Wealdstone F.C.|Wealdstone]]\n|team13=LEA|name_LEA=[[Leamington F.C.|Lockheed Leamington]]\n|team14=GLO|name_GLO=[[Gloucester City A.F.C.|Gloucester City]]\n|team15=STE|name_STE=[[Stevenage Athletic F.C.|Stevenage Athletic]]\n|team16=BLE|name_BLE=[[Bletchley Town F.C.|Bletchley Town]]\n|team17=DUN|name_DUN=[[Dunstable Town F.C.|Dunstable Town]]\n|team18=BAR|name_BAR=[[Barry Town United F.C.|Barry Town]]\n|win_KET=23|draw_KET=6|loss_KET=5|gf_KET=70|ga_KET=27\n|win_BTA=18|draw_BTA=13|loss_BTA=3|gf_BTA=58|ga_BTA=27\n|win_CHT=20|draw_CHT=4|loss_CHT=10|gf_CHT=72|ga_CHT=51\n|win_RUG=18|draw_RUG=7|loss_RUG=9|gf_RUG=82|ga_RUG=36\n|win_WEL=15|draw_WEL=10|loss_WEL=9|gf_WEL=73|ga_WEL=44\n|win_STB=13|draw_STB=14|loss_STB=7|gf_STB=59|ga_STB=42\n|win_KIN=14|draw_KIN=11|loss_KIN=9|gf_KIN=62|ga_KIN=45\n|win_COR=15|draw_COR=9|loss_COR=10|gf_COR=47|ga_COR=35\n|win_ILK=14|draw_ILK=11|loss_ILK=9|gf_ILK=44|ga_ILK=38\n|win_BAN=14|draw_BAN=5|loss_BAN=15|gf_BAN=54|ga_BAN=46\n|win_BRY=14|draw_BRY=5|los